    <title>LaTex在Markdown中的基础应用</title>
    <url>/2020/04/02/LaTex%E5%9C%A8Markdown%E4%B8%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>LaTex是一种基于TEX的排版系统，常用于论文写作等方面。Typora默认支持LaTex公式，但是需要掌握基础的语法<a id="more"></a></p>
<h3 id="数学运算"><a href="#数学运算" class="headerlink" title="数学运算"></a>数学运算</h3><table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>格式</th>
<th align="left">效果</th>
<th>语法</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td>上标</td>
<td align="left">$ x^2 $</td>
<td><code>$x^2$</code></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>下标</td>
<td align="left">$y_1$</td>
<td><code>$y_1$</code></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>左右分式</td>
<td align="left">$1/2$</td>
<td><code>$1/2$</code></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>上下分式</td>
<td align="left">$\frac{1}{2}$</td>
<td><code>$\frac{1}{2}$</code></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>省略号</td>
<td align="left">$\cdots$</td>
<td><code>$\cdots$</code></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>开根号</td>
<td align="left">$\sqrt{2}$</td>
<td><code>$\sqrt{2}$</code></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>矢量</td>
<td align="left">$\vec{a}$</td>
<td><code>$\vec{a}$</code></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>积分</td>
<td align="left">$\int_{1}^{2}xdx$</td>
<td><code>$\int_{1}^{2}xdx$</code></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>极限</td>
<td align="left">$\lim{a+b}$</td>
<td><code>$\lim{a+b}$</code></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td></td>
<td align="left">$\lim_{n\rightarrow+\infty}$</td>
<td><code>$\lim_{n\rightarrow+\infty}$</code></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>累加</td>
<td align="left">$\sum{a}$</td>
<td><code>$\sum{a}$</code></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td></td>
<td align="left">$\sum_{n=1}^{100}{a_n}$</td>
<td><code>$\sum_{n=1}^{100}{a_n}$</code></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>累乘</td>
<td align="left">$\prod{x}$</td>
<td><code>$\prod{x}$</code></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td></td>
<td align="left">$\prod_{n=1}^{99}{x_n}$</td>
<td><code>$\prod_{n=1}^{99}{x_n}$</code></td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<p><strong>综合演示：</strong></p>
<p><code>$\frac{1}{\pi}=\frac{2\sqrt{2}}{9801}\sum^{\infty}_{k=0}\frac{(4k)!(1103+26390k)}{(k!)^4396^{4k}}$</code></p>
